        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[疑问]#月经提前和推迟哪个更健康#月经提前或推迟是指，月经提前或推后超过7天。以上一次的出血日，和下一次初次出血日的前一天计算，只要周期在21-35天之间，都...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9C%88%E7%BB%8F%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%BF%9F%E5%93%AA%E4%B8%AA%E6%9B%B4%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%9C%88%E7%BB%8F%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%BF%9F%E5%93%AA%E4%B8%AA%E6%9B%B4%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#月经提前和推迟哪个更健康#</span></a><br><br>月经提前或推迟是指，月经提前或推后超过7天。以上一次的出血日，和下一次初次出血日的前一天计算，只要周期在21-35天之间，都是正常的。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%9C%88%E7%BB%8F%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%BF%9F%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%9C%88%E7%BB%8F%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%BF%9F%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E7%8E%B0%E8%B1%A1%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#月经提前和推迟都是正常现象#</span></a>，它容易受到情绪、运动、饮食等因素影响，所以偶尔会“迟到早来”。<br><br>各位姐妹，我们要保持好心态，做个情绪稳定的成年人，多锻炼、规律作息，大多能自行恢复。但如果阴道莫名其妙出血，或者月经“乱来”，还是要尽早就医。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（科普中国、深圳市妇幼保健院）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hn14s45u1pj20u00u0acu.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
